message:
Good byes are not forever;
Are not the end;
It simply means we'll miss you until we meet again!

Students' Alumni Cell heartily invites the graduating batch of 2019 for Alvida, the Annual Farewell Dinner. Come, be a part of a lovely evening. 

16th April | Kalidas Auditorium | 7:00 p.m.

